<br>
1) As stated above, either type /pet get lost  and then wait until the casting bar is almost done before hitting enter, or use the Get Lost button on the pet window.<br>
<br>
2) I will occasionally chaincast on the guards in katta using 57 earth. Earth is probably the best pet to learn this skill on as the root effect can buy you some time to get away if you mess up. I typically wait until I see that the pet is nearing one bub of hp, and I see a root message land before I start casting the next pet. If I don't see a root message around that time, I heal the pet instead.<br>
<br>
