<br>
/cast 1<br>
/cast 1<br>
/pause <br>
/pet get lost<br>
<br>
If the first one fizzles,  the second one PROBABLY won't.  If the first one doesn't fizzle, the second one returns an error to your chat windows, and the macro continues...<br>
<br>
I haven't used it for chaining but it works really well for my paladin's heal macro! :-)<br>
